API changes:
- pmemcto_set_root_pointer() - validate root pointer; return -1 if invalid
- pmemcto_strndup() - same as strndup(), but copies at most n bytes
- pmemcto_extend() - expands pmemcto pool in run time (fallocate + remap)
- pmemcto_flush() - partially flushes pmemcto pool; async flush (???)
- pmemcto_mallctl() - introspecting memory allocator; setting modifiable params
